sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3

SELECT "custom_filter_keywords"."id" AS t0_r0, "custom_filter_keywords"."custom_filter_id" AS t0_r1, "custom_filter_keywords"."keyword" AS t0_r2, "custom_filter_keywords"."whole_word" AS t0_r3, "custom_filter_keywords"."created_at" AS t0_r4, "custom_filter_keywords"."updated_at" AS t0_r5, "custom_filter"."id" AS t1_r0, "custom_filter"."account_id" AS t1_r1, "custom_filter"."expires_at" AS t1_r2, "custom_filter"."phrase" AS t1_r3, "custom_filter"."context" AS t1_r4, "custom_filter"."created_at" AS t1_r5, "custom_filter"."updated_at" AS t1_r6, "custom_filter"."action" AS t1_r7 FROM "custom_filter_keywords" LEFT OUTER JOIN "custom_filters" "custom_filter" ON "custom_filter"."id" = "custom_filter_keywords"."custom_filter_id" WHERE "custom_filter"."account_id" = $1
